{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-466-distinct-terms-in-a-multiplication-table","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 466: Različite reči u tablici za množenje","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka $P(m,n)$ bude broj različitih reči u tabeli množenja $m \\times n$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, tablica za množenje 3×4 izgleda ovako:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{array}{c}\n×          &#x26; \\mathbf{1} &#x26; \\mathbf{2} &#x26; \\mathbf{3} &#x26; \\mathbf{4}  \\\\\n\\mathbf{1} &#x26; 1          &#x26; 2          &#x26; 3          &#x26; 4  \\\\\n\\mathbf{2} &#x26; 2          &#x26; 4          &#x26; 6          &#x26; 8  \\\\\n\\mathbf{3} &#x26; 3          &#x26; 6          &#x26; 9          &#x26; 12\n\\end{array}$$</p>\n<p>Postoji osam različitih reči {1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 8, 9, 12}, stoga $P(3, 4) = 8$.</p>\n<p>Dano je da:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; P(64, 64) = 1\\,263, \\\\\n&#x26; P(12, 345) = 1\\,998, \\text{ na} \\\\\n&#x26; P(32, {10}^{15}) = 13\\,826\\,382\\,602\\,124\\,302. \\\\\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Pronađi $P(64, {10}^{16})$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f53e1000cf542c510051","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302141,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-466-distinct-terms-in-a-multiplication-table"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function multiplicationTable() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nmultiplicationTable();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>multiplicationTable()</code> tr